{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013500/extras/about_the_game.png?t=1735331051\" /><br><br>&quot;Bunny Space Odyssey: FlopHop&quot; is an adventure pixel art indie game with platformer and puzzle elements. You will play as Ponchee the bunny, who finds herself on an uninhabited planet called FlopHop. She has no memories except for current events, and her teacher and friend becomes her spacesuit Usagi-01, which tells her about the past, the future, and her destiny.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013500/extras/planetgif.gif?t=1735331051\" /><br><br>Gameplay<br>In the world of FlopHop, you will experience an exciting story told through quests and lore, during which you will be engaged in platforming gameplay: Ponchee must protect capsules with plants to eventually green the planet. You will also encounter many puzzles of various kinds that will stand in Ponchee's way as she learns about the history of the world, the universe, and her home planet.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013500/extras/cavegif.gif?t=1735331051\" /><br><br>Why is Ponchee alone on this planet? Who created Usagi-01? What happened to her home planet, and how did she end up on FlopHop? Ponchee will uncover all this together with our players! But this journey of discovery might not be so sweet \u2013 along the way, there will be many disappointments, moments of loneliness, contemplation, and reflection.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735331051","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013500/page.bg.jpg?t=1735331051","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013500/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735331051","capsule_imagev5":"h